People's Daily Commentator: A good start for the 14th Five-Year Plan -- On Learning and Implementing the Spirit of the Central Economic Work Conference-Xinhua News
Xinhua News Agency, Beijing, December 11th - An article by the People's Daily commentator on December 12th: "A Good Start to the 14th Five-Year Plan - On Learning and Implementing the Spirit of the Central Economic Work Conference
The Central Economic Work Conference, held from December 8 to 10, highly evaluated the achievements of China's economic and social development in the past year, realizing a good start for the 14th Five-Year Plan.
General Secretary Xi Jinping delivered an important speech at the meeting, profoundly summarizing the economic work of 2021, deeply analyzing the current economic situation, making important deployments for the economic work of 2022, and providing fundamental guidance for us to do well in the economic work of next year and to welcome the successful convening of the Party's Twentieth National Congress.
We solemnly celebrate the centennial of the founding of the Communist Party of China, officially announce the completion of the first goal of building a moderately prosperous society and the beginning of a new journey towards the second centennial goal of realizing socialist modernization.
We convened the Sixth Plenary Session of the 19th Central Committee of the Communist Party of China, summing up the major achievements and historical experiences of the Party's hundred-year struggle, and passed the third historical resolution in the history of the Party "Resolution of the Central Committee of the Communist Party of China on Major Achievements and Historical Experiences of the Hundred-year Struggle of the Party ". This is a political declaration of the new era Chinese Communist Party members to remember the mission and adhere to and develop Chinese socialism, and an action guide for learning from history, creating the future and realizing the great rejuvenation of the Chinese nation.
In the past year, the world has been facing unprecedented changes and the global epidemic of the novel coronavirus, with a more complicated and difficult external environment, and the heavy and arduous tasks of epidemic prevention and control, as well as economic and social development at home.
The Party Central Committee with Comrade Xi Jinping as the core firmly maintain the overall situation of both domestic and international affairs, persist in the general principle of steady progress while seeking progress, remaining calm and composed in the face of the century-old changes and the century-long epidemic, coordinating the prevention and control of epidemic with the economic and social development, accelerating the building of a new development pattern, strengthening the macro-policy with cross-cycle regulation, making efforts to promote sustainable and healthy economic development, deepening reform, opening up and innovation, striving to complete major tasks in reform and development, and making new major achievements in various undertakings of the Party and the state.
"The 14th Five-Year Plan has made a good start, one important aspect of which is that new strides have been made in constructing a new development pattern, and new achievements have been made in high-quality development."
Our country's economic development and epidemic prevention and control maintain a global leading position, with the characteristics of strong resilience, great potential and adequate power continuing to show; the national strategic scientific and technological strength accelerates its growth and major innovative results emerge one after another, the scientific and technological innovation capability continues to increase, and breakthroughs in key core technologies are achieved; the resilience of the industrial chain is improved, the volume and quality of foreign trade increases, the structure continues to be optimized, and new kinetic energy represented by new industries, new business forms and new models grows and thrives; reform and opening up continues to be deepened, efforts are made to unblock the bottlenecks of the supply-demand matching and factor flow, and high-level opening up is used to create new advantages of cooperation and competition; living security guarantees are effective and the employment scale continues to expand, and the income growth of residents is basically synchronized with the economic growth, with grain production above 130 billion jin for seven consecutive years and a bumper harvest of 18 consecutive years; ecological civilization construction continues to be promoted, carbon peaking and carbon neutrality are coordinated and pushed forward, and green and low-carbon transformation makes steady progress, and new achievements are made in ecological environment protection.
The achievement of these results is the result of the strong leadership of the Party Central Committee with Comrade Xi Jinping at its core, the result of the scientific guidance of Xi Jinping's thoughts on socialism with Chinese characteristics in the new era, and the result of the whole Party, the people of all nationalities throughout the country, working together and striving hard.
Practice has once again verified that it is of decisive significance to the development of the Party and national cause and the progress of the great rejuvenation of the Chinese nation to firmly establish Comrade Xi Jinping as the core of the Party Central Committee and the whole Party and to uphold the guidance of Xi Jinping Thought on Socialism with Chinese Characteristics in the New Era.
With General Secretary Xi Jinping at the core of the Party Central Committee and the entire Party, guiding the nation, with Xi Jinping's Thought on Socialism with Chinese Characteristics for a New Era as scientific guidance, and all the people of China of all ethnic groups, united in one mind, working hard and persevering, we will definitely overcome all kinds of difficulties and hardships and create a new era of brilliance and forge new great historical feats in the new journey of building a socialist modernized country.
Next year will convene the Party’s Twentieth National Congress, which is a major event in the political life of the Party and the nation.
Promote the great spirit of the founding party, adhere to the general tone of seeking stability while making progress, implement the new development concept in an integral, accurate and comprehensive way, speed up the construction of a new development pattern, comprehensively deepen the reform and opening-up, adhere to innovation-driven development, promote high-quality development, adhere to supply-side structural reform as the main line, coordinate epidemic prevention and control and economic and social development, coordinate development and security, continue to do a good job of "six stability" and "six guarantees", and continue to improve people's livelihood. Stabilize the macroeconomic situation, keep the economic operation in a reasonable range, maintain social stability, and we will be able to maintain a stable and healthy economic environment, a safe and harmonious social environment and a clean and upright political environment, and welcome the successful holding of the Party's 19th Congress with outstanding achievements.
Let us unite more closely around the Party Central Committee with Comrade Xi Jinping at the core, strengthen our “four consciousness”, firm up our “four self-confidence”, fulfill our “two responsibilities”, continuously improve our judgment and understanding of politics, as well as our capacity to carry out these decisions, and in practical actions ensure the implementation of the Party Central Committee’s decisions and constantly push forward the cause of Socialism with Chinese Characteristics for a New Era.
